  "rationale": "<p>Choice A is correct. Distributing on the right side yields <math><mi>z</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>z</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn></math>. Subtracting <math><mi>z</mi></math> from both sides yields <math><mo>-</mo><mn>6</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>z</mi><mo>+</mo><mn>12</mn></math>. Subtracting 12 yields <math><mo>-</mo><mn>18</mn><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><mi>z</mi></math>, so <math><mi>z</mi><mo>=</mo><mo>-</mo><mn>9</mn></math>.</p><p>Choices B, C, and D result from sign errors or incomplete distribution.</p>",
